item.title: How I Can Delete Runescape Image
item.dc:creator: @badger41 badger41
item.description:
@badger41 wrote:

Youll have to disable the rs logo through client.java

go into client.java and search for

class30_sub2_sub1_sub1.method346(-180, -171, -32357);

you should see this:

            class30_sub2_sub1_sub1.method346(-180, -171, -32357);
            class30_sub2_sub1_sub1 = new Class30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1(aClass44_1053, "logo", 0);
            aClass15_1107.method237(0);
            class30_sub2_sub1_sub1.method348(382 - class30_sub2_sub1_sub1.anInt1440 / 2 - 128, 16083, 18);
            class30_sub2_sub1_sub1 = null;
            Object obj = null;
            Object obj1 = null;
            System.gc();
            return;

comment that whole group of code out by putting // in front of all the lines or just putting /* in the front and */ after the return.
after that compile and run, the rs logo should be gone

P.S: Dont Type With A Capital Letter In The Beginning Of Your Words, It Doesnt Make You Look Smart.
